<i>a rivalry and quickly returned home?</i>

19
00:03:10.106 --> 00:03:11.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But I’m sure things are going well.</i>

20
00:03:12.942 --> 00:03:14.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I hope things go well.</i>

21
00:03:15.987 --> 00:03:18.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Since we came into this world as women,</i>

22
00:03:18.656 --> 00:03:21.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>let’s be happy as women, Nana.</i>

23
00:03:36.507 --> 00:03:37.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nana!

24
00:03:41.888 --> 00:03:45.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I have no intention</i>
<i>of getting back together with you!</i>

25
00:04:25.640 --> 00:04:30.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What are you doing?
These roses must’ve been expensive.

26
00:04:30.478 --> 00:04:34.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
